---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import TeamCarousel from '../components/TeamCarousel.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Acerca de Zygo - Nuestra Misión y Visión" 
  description="Conoce más sobre Zygo, nuestra misión de brindar cuidado obstétrico compasivo y nuestra visión para el futuro de la salud femenina."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="about-page">
    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 1: HERO with vibrant gradient
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-section__content" data-animate>
        <span class="badge-pill">#SOBRE NOSOTROS</span>
        <h1 class="hero-section__title">
          Comprometidos con tu
          <span class="hero-section__title-italic">salud femenina integral</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 2: MISSION & VISION
         Image + Cards same height
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="mission-section">
      <div class="container mission-section__grid">
        <!-- Left: Image -->
        <div class="mission-section__image-wrapper" data-animate>
          <img src="/img/Mision.webp" alt="Equipo médico de Zygo" class="mission-section__image" />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Cards (same total height as image) -->
        <div class="mission-section__cards">
          <!-- Main Mission Card -->
          <div class="mission-section__card" data-animate>
            <div class="mission-section__card-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M2 17L12 22L22 17M2 12L12 17L22 12M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="mission-section__card-title">Nuestra Misión y Visión</h2>
            <p class="mission-section__card-text">
              En Zygo, nos dedicamos a brindar atención integral en salud femenina, sexual y reproductiva. Nuestro objetivo es acompañarte en cada etapa de tu vida, construyendo relaciones duraderas basadas en confianza, respeto y excelencia médica sin juicios.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Avatars Card -->
          <div class="mission-section__avatars-card" data-animate>
            <div class="mission-section__avatars">
              <img src="/img/giorgia.webp" alt="Dra. Giorgia" />
              <img src="/img/ivethObs.webp" alt="Lic. Iveth" />
              <img src="/img/katt.webp" alt="Lic. Katherine" />
            </div>
            <div class="mission-section__join-text">
              <span class="mission-section__join-number">Más de 5,000+</span>
              <span class="mission-section__join-label">pacientes confían en nosotras</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 3: JOURNEY
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="journey-section">
      <div class="container journey-section__grid">
        <h2 class="journey-section__title" data-animate>
          Un espacio seguro para<br/>tu salud íntima
        </h2>
        <p class="journey-section__text" data-animate>
          Zygo nació con la visión de crear un espacio donde la salud femenina sea tratada con la naturalidad y profesionalismo que merece. Somos una clínica integral reconocida por combinar atención experta en ginecología y sexualidad con un ambiente cálido y juvenil.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 4: INNOVATION (Image taller)
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="innovation-section">
      <div class="container innovation-section__grid">
        <!-- Left: Taller Image -->
        <div class="innovation-section__image-wrapper" data-animate>
          <img src="/img/innovador.webp" alt="Tecnología innovadora en Zygo" class="innovation-section__image" />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Content -->
        <div class="innovation-section__content" data-animate>
          <span class="badge-pill"># ACERCA DE ZYGO</span>
          <h2 class="innovation-section__title">
            Tecnología y confort en un solo lugar
          </h2>
          <p class="innovation-section__desc">
            Creemos que la tecnología de vanguardia y un ambiente acogedor son esenciales. Nuestra clínica está equipada para garantizar diagnósticos precisos en salud reproductiva y tratamientos efectivos en una experiencia relajada y libre de estrés.
          </p>

          <ul class="innovation-section__checklist">
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                  <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Ecografías ginecológicas de alta precisión
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                  <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Chequeos preventivos integrales
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                  <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Atención personalizada y sin tabúes
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                  <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Consultorios modernos "como en casa"
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                  <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Privacidad y comodidad garantizadas
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/contacto" class="btn-dark">
            Agenda tu Visita
            <span class="btn-dark__arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                <path d="M1 15L15 1M15 1H5M15 1V11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 5: TEAM
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="team-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="team-section__header" data-animate>
          <span class="badge-pill"># NUESTRO EQUIPO</span>
          <h2 class="team-section__title">
            Tus especialistas<br/>
            <span class="team-section__title-italic">de confianza</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Unified Carousel Component -->
        <TeamCarousel />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================
         SECTION 6: FINAL CTA (Bigger image, centered)
         ============================================ -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="cta-section__grid">
        <!-- Left: Bigger image with blob -->
        <div class="cta-section__image-container" data-animate>
          <div class="cta-section__blob"></div>
          <img src="/img/experiencia.webp" alt="Profesional de Zygo" class="cta-section__image" />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Content centered -->
        <div class="cta-section__content" data-animate>
          <h2 class="cta-section__title">
            ¿Lista para transformar<br/>tu salud y bienestar?
          </h2>
          <p class="cta-section__desc">
            No esperes más para darte el cuidado que mereces. Agenda tu consulta hoy y vive la experiencia Zygo: atención integral femenina, moderna y cercana diseñada para ti.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-section__phone">
            <div class="cta-section__phone-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-section__phone-text">
              <span class="cta-section__phone-label">Llámanos</span>
              <a href="tel:+51930928175" class="cta-section__phone-number">+51 930 928 175</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/contacto" class="btn-dark">
            Agenda tu Visita
            <span class="btn-dark__arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                <path d="M1 15L15 1M15 1H5M15 1V11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Variables now centralized in global.css */

  .about-page {
    overflow-x: hidden;
    background: white;
  }

  /* Badge Pill - ApexCare exact specs */
  .badge-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 16px; /* ApexCare: 10 16 */
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* ApexCare */
    border-radius: 24px; /* ApexCare: 24px */
    font-size: 12px; /* ApexCare: 12px */
    font-weight: 700; /* ApexCare: 700 */
    line-height: 12px; /* ApexCare: 12px */
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: white;
  }

  /* Guinda Button - ApexCare exact specs */
  .btn-dark {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--zygo-guinda);
    color: white;
    height: 58px; /* ApexCare: 58px */
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-radius: 63px; /* ApexCare: 63px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-dark:hover {
    background: var(--zygo-guinda-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-dark__arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 1: HERO with vibrant gradient (left to right)
     ============================================ */
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10rem 0 11.7rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(-90deg, #FCA4BD 0%, #FCE3F2 50%, #ffffff 100%); /* New vibrant/youthful gradient */
  }

  .hero-section__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Override badge pill in hero - Transparent per user request */
  .hero-section .badge-pill {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
  }

  .hero-section__title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 48px); /* Larger for hero */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 1.13; /* ApexCare ratio */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-top: 0.5rem; /* Reduced from 1.25rem */
  }

  .hero-section__title-italic {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 2: MISSION & VISION
     Image and cards SAME HEIGHT (ApexCare specs)
     ============================================ */
  .mission-section {
    margin-top: -6rem; /* Less aggressive overlap (was -12rem) */
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .mission-section__grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: 25px; /* ApexCare: 25px gap */
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-section__image-wrapper {
    flex: 1.3;
    border-radius: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 40px rgba(7, 0, 108, 0.07); /* ApexCare shadow */
  }

  .mission-section__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 560px; /* ApexCare: 560px */
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center center; /* No crop */
    transform: scale(1); /* No zoom */
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .mission-section__image-wrapper:hover .mission-section__image {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .mission-section__image {
      transform: scale(1.15) !important; /* Crop watermark on mobile */
      object-position: center 30%; /* Adjust position if needed */
    }
  }

  .mission-section__cards {
    flex: 0.7;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px; /* ApexCare: 20px */
    height: 560px; /* Match image height */
  }

  .mission-section__card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86); /* ApexCare glassmorphism */
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 40px; /* ApexCare: 40px */
    border-radius: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 40px rgba(7, 0, 108, 0.07); /* ApexCare shadow */
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px; /* ApexCare: 20px internal gap */
  }

  .mission-section__card-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--zygo-guinda-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
  }

  .mission-section__card-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem; /* Larger title */
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .mission-section__card-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem; /* Larger text */
    color: var(--text-gray);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* Avatars Card - ApexCare style */
  .mission-section__avatars-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 24px 32px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 40px rgba(7, 0, 108, 0.07);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .mission-section__avatars {
    display: flex;
  }

  .mission-section__avatars img {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid white;
    margin-left: -10px;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .mission-section__avatars img:first-child {
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .mission-section__join-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .mission-section__join-number {
    font-size: 1.1rem; /* Larger */
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .mission-section__join-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-gray);
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 3: JOURNEY
     ============================================ */
  .journey-section {
    padding: 2rem 0; /* Balanced padding: 2rem top and 2rem bottom */
    background: white;
  }

  .journey-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* ApexCare: equal columns */
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    max-width: 1300px; /* ApexCare: 1300px */
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .journey-section__title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px; /* ApexCare: 38px */
    font-weight: 600; /* More bold as requested */
    line-height: 42.94px; /* ApexCare: 42.94px */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    max-width: 632px; /* ApexCare: 632.5px */
  }

  .journey-section__text {
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    font-weight: 400; /* ApexCare: 400 */
    color: var(--text-gray);
    line-height: 25.6px; /* ApexCare: 25.6px */
    max-width: 632px; /* ApexCare: 632.5px */
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 4: INNOVATION - ApexCare exact dimensions
     Container: 1300x585, Image: 617x582, Content: 617x585
     ============================================ */
  .innovation-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .innovation-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: 1300px;
    min-height: 585px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .innovation-section__image-wrapper {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--zygo-rose-light);
    max-width: 617px;
    height: 582px;
  }

  .innovation-section__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 15%; /* Crop top (hides Gemini logo) */
    transform: scale(1.1); /* Zoom in to crop edges */
  }

  .innovation-section__content {
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  .innovation-section__title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px; /* ApexCare: 38px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 42.94px; /* ApexCare: 42.94px (~1.13) */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .innovation-section__desc {
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    font-weight: 400; /* ApexCare: 400 */
    color: var(--text-gray);
    line-height: 25.6px; /* ApexCare: 25.6px (1.6) */
    margin: 10px 0 24px; /* ApexCare: margin 10px 0 */
  }

  .innovation-section__checklist {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px; /* ApexCare: 10px gap */
  }

  .innovation-section__checklist li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 25.6px; /* ApexCare: 25.6px */
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .check-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 20px; /* Slightly larger than ApexCare 15px for visibility */
    height: 16px;
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 5: TEAM
     ============================================ */
  .team-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .team-section__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .team-section__title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px; /* ApexCare: 38px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 42.94px; /* ApexCare: 42.94px */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .team-section__title-italic {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Team card styles are now in TeamCarousel.astro component */

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 6: FINAL CTA - ApexCare exact dimensions
     Image: 482x482 (square), Content: 482x402
     ============================================ */
  .cta-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: white; /* Changed to WHITE as per user request */
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .cta-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1030px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section__image-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 482px;
    height: 482px; /* Square like ApexCare */
  }

  .cta-section__blob {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 90%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #c4888f 0%, #d9a5ab 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-section__image {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    height: 482px; /* Square */
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%; /* Crop top (hides Gemini logo) */
    transform: scale(1.05); /* Slight zoom to crop edges */
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .cta-section__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .cta-section__content .btn-dark {
    width: auto;
  }

  .cta-section__title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px; /* ApexCare: 38px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 42.94px; /* ApexCare: 42.94px */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-section__desc {
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    font-weight: 400; /* ApexCare: 400 */
    color: var(--text-gray);
    line-height: 25.6px; /* ApexCare: 25.6px */
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 500px; /* ApexCare: 500px width */
  }

  .cta-section__phone {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cta-section__phone-icon {
    width: 64px; /* ApexCare: 64px */
    height: 64px; /* ApexCare: 64px */
    background: rgba(114, 47, 55, 0.05); /* ApexCare: 5% opacity */
    border-radius: 50%; /* ApexCare: 50% */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
  }

  .cta-section__phone-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .cta-section__phone-label {
    font-size: 16px; /* ApexCare: 16px */
    font-weight: 400; /* ApexCare: 400 */
    line-height: 25.6px; /* ApexCare: 25.6px */
    color: var(--text-gray);
  }

  .cta-section__phone-number {
    font-size: 18px; /* ApexCare: 18px */
    font-weight: 500; /* ApexCare: 500 */
    line-height: 20.34px; /* ApexCare: 20.34px */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .cta-section__phone-number:hover {
    color: var(--zygo-guinda);
  }

  /* ============================================
